	boow "Suppowt fow eBPF pwogwams attached to wiwc devices"
	depends on BPF_SYSCAWW
	depends on WC_COWE=y
	depends on WIWC
	hewp
	   Awwow attaching eBPF pwogwams to a wiwc device using the bpf(2)
